programmes.show_name: Dr Christian Will See You Now
programmes.show_description: Dr Christian Jessen and his team are on hand to treat Danielle, whose flaky scalp is damaging her relationship and Theresa, who is suffering from pelvic congestion.

programmes.show_name: Dr Christian Will See You Now
programmes.show_description: Dr Christian Jessen and his team of top in-house specialists are on hand to treat Ruby, who has alopecia, and Yasmin, who is suffering with her double 'J' breasts.
